                    <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Looks like you haven't added anything yet</p>
                    <a href="/products" @@click="cartOpen = false" class="inline-block bg-fashion-black dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-fashion-black px-8 py-3 uppercase tracking-widest text-sm font-medium hover:bg-primary-600 dark:hover:bg-primary-400 transition">
                        Start Shopping
